		"description": "<p>Beginning at level 10, your supernatural transformation takes on an even more powerful aspect. Your very flesh transforms into lava while you rage, making you even more durable. You are immune to fire damage, and while you are raging, treat critical hits that you suffer as normal hits.&nbsp;</p><p>Additionally, while you are raging, any creature that grapples you, that you grapple, or that begins its turn grappling or grappled by you takes 1d6 fire damage as the searing heat of your molten insides burns it.&nbsp;</p><p>Finally, while you are raging, you may ignite flammable materials with a touch as a bonus action.</p>",
